ACT:
 Tortious liability of State for damages for trespass and unauthorised intereference by if with the proprietory interest and negligence-Effect of Section 31 of the Bihar State Management of Estates and Tenures Act 1949-Act done in good faith-Whether Section 31 of the Act read with Section 4 (22) of the Bihar and Orissa General Clauses Act 1917 protects such State action against and alleged claim for loss by wilful default or gross negligence.
 
